(a1) pinoxaden;
or (a2) florasulam or an agrochemically acceptable salt thereof;
or (a2a) metosulam or an agrochemically acceptable salt thereof;
or (a2b) diclosulam or an agrochemically acceptable salt thereof;
or (a2c) cloransulam-methyl;
or (a3) clodinafop-propargyl;
or a combination of (a2) florasulam or an agrochemically acceptable salt thereof with (a1) pinoxaden and/or (a3) clodinafop-propargyl;
or a combination of (a2a) metosulam or an agrochemically acceptable salt thereof with (a1)) pinoxaden and/or (a3) clodinafop-propargyl;
